sourcesContent: import React, {Fragment} from 'react'; import { Button } from '../buttons/Button.jsx'; import { InfoContainer, InfoWrapper, InfoRow, Column1, TextWrapper, TopLine, Heading, Subtitle, BtnWrap, Column2, ImgWrap, Img } from './InfoElements'; const Info = ({lightBg, id, imgStart, topLine, lightText, headline, darkText, description, buttonLabel, img, alt}) => { return ( <> {topLine} {headline} {description} ) } export default Info;
